Project Description
The Collective Network Silverlight Template is a silverlight template that is designed as a starting point for the development of line of business applications that requires access control for users.

This project is currently in development.

System requirements are;
  • Silverlight 5
  • Microsoft SQL 2008 R2
  • Visual Studio 2010
